Key Executives
                > Matthew V. Hollifield
            
Matthew V. Hollifield, Senior Vice President and Chief Accounting Officer



Profile
Connections






Biography



    Matthew V. Hollifield, Senior Vice President and Chief Accounting Officer since 2005; Vice President, Corporate Accounts Payables 2002-2005. Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Century Furniture Industries, 2000-2002. Mr. Hollifield received a Masters in Business Administration degree from Duke University and a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration degree from Appalachian State University. Mr. Hollifield is a certified public accountant.
    





Board Membership




Matthew V. Hollifield is not a member of any boards




 


  







